@oppositeofred Hi there, 
Thank you for getting in touch. Please send us your booking code, so we can take a closer look.
Best regards, Shawn

@gags3005 Hi Gagan, 
We are sorry for the inconvenience caused during your journey. Please send us your claim via our web page. Please use the following link https://t.co/xzbXsPK1br and fill out the online form. Our colleagues will take care of this matter. 
Best regards, Shawn

@aka_Jewlz Hi Michael, 
We are sorry for all the trouble caused. Please use the following email address to contact our colleagues via mail: viellos@austrian.com
Best regards, Shawn

@balloonsdontpo1 Hi there, 
We can't offer you any phone number, however, you can contact them via the following email address: viellos@austrian.com. Thank you for your patience and understanding.
Best regards, Shawn

@steverechtman Hi Steve, 
Thank you for getting in touch. Please send us your booking code, so we can take a closer look. 
Best regards, Shawn

@elha2060 Dear Elias,
the Social Media Team does not have access to the baggage system. Please get in touch with the phone number on your lost baggage report or you can check the status of your baggage online via this link https://t.co/hrzpeJ2rHC 
Best regards, Alessandra

@Didulou Dear Elodie,
sorry to hear that. The Social Media Team does not have access to the baggage system. Please get in touch with the phone number on your lost baggage report or you can check the status of your baggage online via this link https://t.co/hrzpeJ2rHC 
Best regards, Alessa

@Ahmed74555770 Dear Ahmed,
we're sorry to hear your bag has been delayed. Our Baggage team will do all they can to reunite you with it as soon as possible. 
Best regards, Alessandra

@ZMSOXCAPITAL Hallo,
wir haben hier auf Twitter keinen Zugriff auf die Gepäcksysteme und können daher in diesem Fall leider nicht weiterhelfen. Bitte bleibe in Kontakt mit dem zuständigen Team von Lost &amp; Found. 
Viele Grüße, Alessandra
